      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Document the physical movement of materials (raw materials, fabricated components, manufactured subassemblies, required ingredients, or intermediate formulations) from a stocking location to a specific point of use location. Issuing material includes the corresponding system transaction. The bill of material, routing information or production instructions will determine the materials to be issued to support the manufacturing operation(s). This activity follows the tasks associated with receiving material from a supplier (P-070 Receive Materials &amp; Services from Suppliers) and any kitting efforts required (L-040 Develop and Assemble Kits). "/>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-approvedby" metaValue="[&quot;Shilpa Chandra&quot;]"/>
